    • getMediaOffsetExpires

      @Deprecated public int getMediaOffsetExpires()
      Deprecated.
      Use getMediaMaxAge() instead
      Returns the offset, the Expires http header of media is set into the future. Together with a http reverse proxy this ensures, that for that time no request for that data will reach the servlet. This may reduce the load on the server. If zero, no Expires header is sent.
